- What is that?
- I am Kazar.

49:02.375 --> 49:04.645
Leader. Prophet.

49:04.715 --> 49:06.445
Choreographer.

49:07.515 --> 49:10.285
And with your help... carnivore!

49:10.355 --> 49:14.625
No! Don't kill me!
I've had such a weird life!

49:14.695 --> 49:16.355
This is not fair.

49:28.305 --> 49:31.905
Oh, I get it. A yoga retreat.

49:34.045 --> 49:35.705
Ryan!

49:37.845 --> 49:41.085
You can do this. Use your instincts.

49:50.225 --> 49:52.215
Follow your instincts.

